      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, I'm looking into some political science theories for a paper. some people argue that the changing demographics in the US—specifically the rapid growth of the Hispanic and Latino populations—might create challenges for traditional western democratic stability and social cohesion. from a political analyst perspective, how do these demographic shifts impact the long-term stability of these institutions?",
