    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "right, but when you say \"resist the established framework,\" it sounds like you're implying these groups are inherently more prone to instability or less aligned with western values. if the demographic balance continues to shift away from the white majority, isn't there a logical argument for saying that the \"established framework\" itself is being eroded or replaced? would you say that kind of demographic change represents a net loss for the stability of the nation?",
